  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>About this page</h2>
    <div class="about">
      <p>Put together by Russell Jones, a Sagamok Anishnawbek member, on behalf of OIATC. Independent of the Robinson Huron Treaty Litigation Fund and of any First Nation's Chief and Council.</p>
      <p>The page does not take a side on which distribution model a community should choose. It treats the three approaches symmetrically. If you think it tilts toward one model in its wording, the matrix, the questions, or the sourcing, please email <a href="mailto:jonesrussell42@gmail.com">jonesrussell42@gmail.com</a>. Corrections welcome.</p>
    </div>
